					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="How a Big Birthday Inspired One Man to Become a Franchisee" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160304164141-master-destiny.jpeg" rel="share" />

